ZH: 他每天早上都服用一粒维生素片。
EN: He takes a vitamin pill every morning.

ZH: 请按照医生的建议服用这种药。
EN: Please take this medication as prescribed by the doctor.

ZH: 这种药必须空腹服用。
EN: This medication must be taken on an empty stomach.

ZH: 务必按时服用药物。
EN: It is important to take the medicine on time.

ZH: 他因为感冒需要服用退烧药。
EN: He needs to take fever-reducing medicine because he has a cold.

ZH: 请在食物的过程中服用这种补充剂。
EN: Please take this supplement during meals.

ZH: 身体没有问题，只要按时服用药物。
EN: There is nothing wrong with the body, just take the medicine on time.

ZH: 咖啡因会影响睡眠，所以晚上不要服用。
EN: Caffeine can affect sleep, so do not take it at night.

ZH: 您应该坚持服用这种药物直到症状消失。
EN: You should continue taking this medication until the symptoms disappear.

ZH: 这种药只能口服，不能注射。
EN: This medication can only be taken orally, not by injection.

ZH: 他每天都要服用抗生素。
EN: He has to take antibiotics every day.

ZH: 请确保按照正确的剂量服用药物。
EN: Make sure to take the medication in the correct dosage.

ZH: 心脏病患者需要服用降压药。
EN: Heart patients need to take blood pressure medication.

ZH: 服用药物前最好先吃东西。
EN: It's best to eat something before taking medication.

ZH: 养成每天定时服用药物的习惯。
EN: Develop a habit of taking medication at the same time every day.

ZH: 这种药需要餐后服用。
EN: This medication should be taken after meals.

ZH: 不要随便改变药物的服用方式。
EN: Do not change the way you take medication without permission.

ZH: 他已经停止服用抗生素。
EN: He has stopped taking antibiotics.

ZH: 如果有不适，请及时停止服用药物。
EN: If you feel unwell, stop taking the medication immediately.

ZH: 患者需要按照处方服用药物。
EN: Patients need to take medication according to the prescription.
